snippet.title: Kunitsu-Gami: Path of the Goddess - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Don't miss this brand new Kunitsu-Gami: Path of the Goddess gameplay from the upcoming Japanese-inspired, single-player action strategy game. 
Kunitsu-Gami: Path of the Goddess is coming to PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, and PC on July 19, 2024.
